---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = 'April 2025';
---

<Layout title="Now" description="What Khoi is currently working on.">

  <div class="pt-40 pb-32 px-6 md:px-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">

      <div class="mb-16 pb-8 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]">
        <p class="animate-fade-up font-display font-light text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-6">Now</p>
        <h1 class="animate-fade-up animate-fade-up-delay-1 font-display font-light text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-[var(--color-ink)]">
          What I'm doing now.
        </h1>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal prose">
        <p>
          Updated {updated} from Texas.
        </p>

        <h2>Building</h2>
        <p>
          Working on a new project — still in early days, focused on getting the core right before anything else.
        </p>

        <h2>Studying</h2>
        <p>
          Finishing up the semester at Texas A&M. Juggling coursework with building, which is harder than it sounds and more valuable than it seems.
        </p>

        <h2>Reading</h2>
        <p>
          Currently reading — update this as you go. Fiction, nonfiction, it all counts.
        </p>

        <h2>Thinking about</h2>
        <p>
          What makes a product actually good. The gap between clever and useful. How to build something worth building.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
          This is a <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank" rel="noopener">now page</a> — a snapshot of what I'm focused on at this point in time.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
